## Notes

- Start on MT5 demo only.
- Keep `EXECUTION__DRY_RUN=true` until the whole path is validated end-to-end.
- Daily loss guard is enforced from equity snapshots, not just closed trade PnL.
- Spread filtering and retry logic are built in, but you still need broker-specific tuning.
